{
  "stem": "2350.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then we, we start smelling the flesh.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then when we realized, she says, your mothers and fathers and children are dead.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Then I realized that I lost my mother because they says they're taking away the mothers and the children in a different place.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So I says, now this is the end.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So every day, we were watching, every night how the chimney was burning all the people.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Every day, transports were coming.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And were burning-- the chimneys were burning.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And we were going on the [NON-ENGLISH] and coming back to the block rain or shine, every day.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Most of the people-- there were almost every second day selections.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Whoever fell, fell.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They took you away.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Whoever they didn't like, they put away.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Whoever survived, survived.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was walking down from this upstairs down.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was stepping every morning on deads.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Here was somebody that I knew.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Here was somebody older that died, a mother of some, of a friend of mine.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You know, coming down, you didn't know every morning, where are the deads.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So life-- we-- I was on, on the quarantine they called at Birkenau-- quarantined for four months.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Normally, people did not survive four months, because either you survived two, three weeks, and they took you to work right away, or you were dying or you were dead.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You went to, to, to the oven.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They kept us four months there, from August 26 till Christmas.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we were going through hell.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The winter came.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They gave us the wooden shoes from Holland.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's why I bought a pair of Holland shoes, and I keep it in my car for a souvenir.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we walked, and they were rubbing our feet because this was not comfortable.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
